- Suggested next task id: `AUTH-CONTEXT-TRUST-BOUNDARY-001`

### RCR-P0-002: query data scope ignores operatorId, roleCodes, and registry dataScopeTemplate

- Severity: P0
- Requirement IDs: `FR-008`, `FR-009`, `AC-008`, `AC-009`
